headline: Does Regency Centers (REG) Price Reflect Growth After Solid Multi‑Year Share Returns?
summary: Investors may be wondering if Regency Centers at around US$71.47 is offering fair value right now, or if the price has run ahead of the underlying business. The stock has returned 2.5% over the last 7 days, 5.0% over the past month, 5.2% year to date, 4.5% over 1 year, 25.6% over 3 years and 86.1% over 5 years, which may have shifted how investors think about both its growth potential and its risks.
